```

### 4.2 Add Category Mapping (if new category)

**Location:** `Flowery.Uno.Gallery/MainView.xaml.cs`

```csharp
_categoryControls = new Dictionary<string, Func<Control>>
{
    // ...existing entries...
    ["New Category"] = () => new NewCategoryExamples()
